      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/5/12",
      "text": [
        ": سمعت أبا جعفر الباقر يقول: كل راية ترفع - أو قال: تخرج - قبل قيام القائم صاحبها طاغوت."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(12) Ali bin Ahmad al-Bandaneeji narrated from Obaydillah bin Musa al-Alawi from Ali bin Ibraheem bin Hisham from his father from Abdullah bin al-Mugheera from Abdullah bin Miskan that Malik bin A’yun al-Juhani had said: “I heard Abu Ja’far al-Baqir (as) saying: Every banner that is raised-or comes out-before the appearance of al-Qa’im (as) will be of an oppressive arrogant.”"
        ]
      }
    },
